    "data": {
      "text": "I've just purchased $VET here as it breaks through the daily and weekly zone. One of the strongest OIL and Gas names today. Stop loss is weekly low (around 5%/pull back aka 1 ADR). Notice how CVX and OXY yanked back when OIL futures pulled in but $VET kept moving. This is the relative strength you want to see. Also notice how it's trying to push through all resistance zones? Clear skies ahead here if it can hold. This is a great example of the trades I take, risking 1-2% of my account and onto the next. Options chain looks nice too. &#x200B; https://preview.redd.it/ceu4joytlaj91.png?width=1934&format=png&auto=webp&s=c035b652115298046c68d94da854860e0cd3b5be https://preview.redd.it/h3nrgoytlaj91.png?width=1934&format=png&auto=webp&s=0470b8bb0ec9ecea54758834416a8c35daef87cc"
